Hangman Game Project Documentation 🎮
1. Project Title

Hangman Game Using Python

2. Introduction

Hangman is a popular word guessing game where the player attempts to guess a hidden word by entering one letter at a time. For every incorrect guess, the player loses one attempt. The game continues until the player correctly guesses the word or runs out of chances.

This project is developed using Python and demonstrates the use of basic programming concepts such as loops, conditions, lists, strings, and randomization.

3. Objective
To develop a simple command-line Hangman Game.
To improve logical thinking and programming skills.
To understand Python fundamentals through a mini project.
To create an interactive and user-friendly game.
4. Technologies Used
