Python 3.x
VS Code / PyCharm / Any Python IDE
7. Working of the Project
The program selects a random word from a predefined list.
Blank spaces are displayed instead of letters.
The user enters one letter at a time.
If the guessed letter is correct:
The letter is revealed in the word.
If the guessed letter is incorrect:
The number of attempts decreases.
The game ends when:
The user guesses the complete word, or
The attempts become zero.
