9. Algorithm
Import the random module.
Create a list of words.
Randomly choose one word.
Initialize:
Empty guessed letters list
Number of attempts
Use a loop until:
Word is guessed OR attempts become zero.
Ask the user to enter a letter.
Check whether the letter exists in the word.
Update display and attempts accordingly.
Display final result.
